videoframeSigmonVm0010MIB.description: This MIB describes the device specific objects of the VM0010 GPO Module, and augments MIB-2, VF-GENERIC, and VF-SIGMON in the identification of this Videoframe Systems managed device. vm0010Table.name: vm0010Table
vm0010Table.description: Each row contains information about one VM0010 GPI Interface module in the managed VF200 frame.

vm0010SlotNumber.name: vm0010SlotNumber
vm0010SlotNumber.description: The slot that this entry represents.

vm0010Active.name: vm0010Active
vm0010Active.description: Indicates whether this entry is active (this module is in this slot).

vm0010Locate.name: vm0010Locate
vm0010Locate.description: Controls the locate indicator on the module and indicates its current state. Set to flash (1) to cause the locate LED on the front of the module to begin flashing. Set to off to stop flashing.

vm0010GPORelayTable.name: vm0010GPORelayTable
vm0010GPORelayTable.description: Each row contains information about one GPO relay of one VM0010 GPO Interface module in the managed VF200 frame.

vm0010GPORelayEntry.name: vm0010GPORelayEntry
vm0010GPORelayEntry.description: A GPI Interface module GPI signal entry.

vm0010GPORelaySlotNumber.name: vm0010GPORelaySlotNumber
vm0010GPORelaySlotNumber.description: The frame slot number that this entry represents.

vm0010GPORelayNumber.name: vm0010GPORelayNumber
vm0010GPORelayNumber.description: The Relay number within the module.

vm0010GPOClosureState.name: vm0010GPOClosureState
vm0010GPOClosureState.description: Controls and indicates the current state of this GPO closure.

vm0010GPOClosureName.name: vm0010GPOClosureName
vm0010GPOClosureName.description: The name of this GPO closure.

vm0010GPOClosureDescription.name: vm0010GPOClosureDescription
vm0010GPOClosureDescription.description: Descriptive identification of this GPO closure.
